Venezuela Economy May Grow More Than 4% in 2011, Mundo Reports

-- B y   J o s e   O r o z c o
-- 
2011-06-06T13:39:24Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-06/venezuela-economy-may-grow-more-than-4-in-2011-mundo-reports.html
Venezuela ’s economy may expand more
than 4 percent in 2011 as the construction industry begins to
grow, public spending is maintained and more importers have
access to foreign currency, central bank director  Armando Leon 
said in an interview with  El Mundo .  Venezuela’a economy contracted 1.7 percent in 2010.  To contact the reporters on this story:
Jose Orozco in Caracas at 
 jorozco8@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
